description:
This data shows the 789 chrysler dealerships that have been announced as dealerships to be closed by 6.9.2009. 

The data comes from huffingtonpost.com. The data includes: Dealership name, majority owner name, dealer address, dealer code, auto lines, and lat/lon location. Lat/lons were determined by geocoding the address at gpsvisualizer.com to get the lat/lon coordinates. 

For auto lines: D = Dodge, T = Dodge Trucks, J = Jeep, C = Chrysler
